Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:08.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦 回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:12.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等下 我今天要做值日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:16.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么啊笨蛋粟屋 我代你做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.04,0:00:18.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦快点回去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:20.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,记得恩恩爱爱地顺路去一下可丽饼店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:24.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:27.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火 现在要回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:28.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:29.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:32.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那要不要一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:36.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,升上二年级也没怎么一起回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:37.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.38,0:00:39.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:43.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊最近是和粟屋一起回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:44.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.96,0:00:46.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.64,0:00:49.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟 是男朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:51.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,男友优先
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:55.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 多谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.98,0:01:00.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 粟屋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:03.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,粟屋也很受欢迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.46,0:01:05.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的挺相衬的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.86,0:01:12.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不和朋友一起回去好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:15.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 给我喝一口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.42,0:01:30.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.50,0:01:34.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吓…了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.44,0:01:40.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:44.00,Kuzu_title1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HE1\t(0,930,0.5,\alpha&H00)\fs150\blur30\t(0,930,2.5,\blur0)\t(0,3000,0.8,\fs105)\pos(1272,585)}有求于那份温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,--------------OP----------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:19.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦和我是住在同一座公寓的青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:22.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:27.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小乃莉子和麦君在一起的话就像公主殿下和王子殿下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:32.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下和王子殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:37.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这句话把年幼的我俘虏住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:40.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:44.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,升上一年级我留长了头发
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:47.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,变得不再和男孩子一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:50.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是收集很多可爱的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.59,0:03:53.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想要成为配得上王子的公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:58.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 明明只要王子回头来看我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:00.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:04.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:08.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是鸥端乃莉子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:09.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:10.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:12.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:14.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是 安乐冈花火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:16.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没骗你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:19.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:23.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…我想起你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:26.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 你认识？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:29.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 鸥鸥鸭鸥来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.57,0:04:30.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太多鸥了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:32.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 乃莉子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:34.25,kuzu_scene6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs105\fad(50,0)\pos(169,563)\c&H464648&}乃莉子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:34.25,kuzu_scene6,,0,0,0,,{\c&H353535&\fs60\fad(50,0)\pos(42,750)}(真名)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:34.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个你倒是上脑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:36.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,鸥端最可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:39.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我名字写作最可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:41.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:42.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别的我都不接受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:47.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是是 还是一如既往的麻烦啊你这人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.99,0:04:52.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是 从以前开始就超让人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:55.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么像你这种人会和麦拍拖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:58.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦也被这种女人骗了真可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.85,0:05:01.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在麦面前也是在装可爱的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:02.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没装啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:04.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 居然发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:08.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 这家伙品行恶劣 颇为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:10.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真不想被你说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:13.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么啊这
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:15.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:18.42,kuzu_scene6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord9\fs105\frz286.2\fad(294,0)\3c&H386CC9&\move(-54,420,208.5,420,0,3089)}感觉真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:18.42,kuzu_scene6,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fs105\frz286.2\move(-54,420,208.5,420,0,3089)\fad(294,0)\3c&HFFFFFF&}感觉真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:18.42,kuzu_scene6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord9\frz286.2\move(-214.5,717,48,717,0,3089)\fad(294,0)}{\fs105\3c&H386CC9&}那种语气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:18.42,kuzu_scene6,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\frz286.2\move(-214.5,717,48,717,0,3089)\fad(294,0)\fs105\3c&HFFFFFF&}那种语气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:19.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 这也是花火她的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:25.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 我也是喜欢麦的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:34.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以请不要未经许可就去勾搭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:37.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他人的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:44.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天的 那家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:47.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不用做到这程度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:52.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那人喜欢你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:54.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:56.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:59.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,倒不如说 为什么不好好甩掉她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:04.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是完全没用那种心思去看她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:06.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是温柔的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:07.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:10.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是因为那人可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:12.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:14.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:16.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:18.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是沉浸于优越感里而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:22.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在奇怪的地方抬杠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:27.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对我有独占欲吗 嫉妒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:29.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别误会了笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:33.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,与占有欲…不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:36.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:39.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的只是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:42.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:47.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:55.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都太拼命了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:58.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太奇怪了啊日本的通勤列车
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:04.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好想快点见到麦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:10.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只能在想念着麦的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是最为痛苦并让人讨厌的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:16.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,渐渐地在自己心中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:24.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不经意地按自己的欲望改写了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:25.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:35.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最可今天也吃面包？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:38.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:41.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,给 甜的和不甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:43.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不说也想要的面包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:46.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦 我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:48.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛 给我放开啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:52.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:52.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 真正见面的时间才是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:55.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为此才会有现在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 便当
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:04.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有炸鸡喔 吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:04.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:07.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,来 啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:13.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,炸鸡块消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:17.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真的啊 灵异现象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:19.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们 别无视我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:20.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,给我适可而唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:24.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我才要说你给我适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:25.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然敢恬不知耻地在午饭时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:28.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像情侣般旁若无人地跟过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:31.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前忠告过你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:33.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真吵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:35.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,野兽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:40.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这性格恶劣的女人 你绝对不是有多喜欢麦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:42.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被利用了啊麦你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:43.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对那女人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:46.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是与帅气的麦在一起就洋洋得意之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:47.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:49.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:52.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 亏你能发现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:54.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们 不要都给我同意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:59.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 我是绝对不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:00.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:03.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不放弃就别逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:05.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:07.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,用的还是敬语
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:09.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真不爽 真不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,利用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:19.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:21.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在走廊上跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:22.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:27.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直想说一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:29.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,走廊可不能跑啊这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:31.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像电视剧动画里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:35.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个为什么我非得帮忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:39.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思让小花以外的人帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:42.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啊真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:46.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 要搬到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到国语准备室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:51.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 不就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.85,0:09:55.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,两人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:59.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,机会 不是独自兴奋的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:00.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}讲义就放在那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:01.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 我应该做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:04.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 真重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:07.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,至少要让哥哥意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:09.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是作为一名「异性」存在的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:25.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,钢琴声
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:34.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:36.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,弹得真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:39.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,经常都能听见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:51.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都成为音乐老师了会弹个钢琴不是理所当然的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:54.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别用麦来说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:57.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如此下去一无所有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:11:01.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,唯有与你甘苦与共
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:04.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,终于我们才会意识
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:08.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那些就已经是全……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:06.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不想放弃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:14.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉更年轻更帅气的大有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:16.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:19.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是在说我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:22.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦你也来唱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:30.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,动摇的心化为汹涌的旋涡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:33.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,相互融解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:38.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,相互融解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:42.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:47.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥是很帅的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:51.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:57.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:12:00.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂的吧 麦你也一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:04.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是放弃不放弃的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:09.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢上一个人 便是非君不可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:10.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:16.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:18.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么喜欢上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:21.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:23.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也不都是痛苦的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.75,0:12:26.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:32.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不会去想「要是不认识的话」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:35.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:39.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:41.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被称作多余的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:47.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:50.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:51.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:12.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,粟屋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:19.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,粟屋 摸下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:24.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:32.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 叫哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 也对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:47.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小麦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:53.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然用你来幻想这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:56.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,并因此感到心安理得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:06.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,索性 你能够痛斥我一顿就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.13,0:14:18.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,性格恶劣的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:21.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你绝对不是有多喜欢麦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:23.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦只是被你利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:27.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,利用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:39.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被利用的是 花火的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:45.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:50.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了花火 你满脸通红的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:52.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,睡过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是完全还来得及嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:56.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:11.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱咨询
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:17.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好的嘛 偶尔这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:18.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看呗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:22.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要说什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:25.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火你没什么女性朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:27.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有 有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:30.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都说有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:32.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:35.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小 小绘等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:37.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只有她一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.03,0:15:41.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才叫你去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:42.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:49.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要接吻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:54.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:57.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:15:59.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:01.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:02.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,搞得像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:07.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像是真正的男朋友一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:14.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天想找你咨询的是她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:19.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这位步美同学和宏是青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:20.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们家住的很近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:23.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到初中时两人就顺理成章的交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:29.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然当时还许下要永远在一起这种天真的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:30.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:31.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:32.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,后来他们上了不同的高中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:34.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小宏轻易的就劈腿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:36.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是步美却无法放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.79,0:16:39.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至自己提出那样也无所谓的备胎宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:42.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这时跟步美同学校的学长注意到了这个情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:42.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:47.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,步美渐渐的被学长的温柔所俘获
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:51.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但果然还是没法跟宏断绝关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:55.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,结果就和宏还有学长同时保持着关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:57.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:00.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就和小宏的作为一样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:02.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:05.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了让她选学长的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:07.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安乐冈也是这样想的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:12.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 这剧情好复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:15.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,步美到底喜欢哪一方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定不了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:22.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,决定不了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:23.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:26.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能和哥哥进展顺利的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就能和麦分手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:30.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦也是这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:34.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉对她们的话题没有共鸣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:38.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 叫你选学长啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:40.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么看都是学长条件更好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:42.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.49,0:17:46.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真的对两人都喜欢的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:48.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,并因此感到痛苦的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:50.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还是都分手斩断痛苦比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.27,0:17:58.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,该说是因为两个人都喜欢才感到痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.38,0:18:02.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说是因为没法决定才感觉痛苦之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:05.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不想自己选错人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:07.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:09.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不想之后再后悔嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:12.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是选学长比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:15.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是小宏更帅嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑到将来的话还是前辈比较好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:20.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小宏的优点就只会运动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:22.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,换成安乐冈同学会选谁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:26.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:33.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 小绘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:35.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.39,0:18:40.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘有喜欢的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:44.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:46.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看来有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.97,0:18:53.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘不会因为那个人的条件好坏而喜欢上那个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:05.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个的话 能力也是那个人的一部分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:09.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不会因为那个人很优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.76,0:19:13.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能给自己带来好处而喜欢上她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:16.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:18.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然我还是最喜欢小绘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:22.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:23.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:26.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢一个人才不是那样的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:33.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟花火有男朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:38.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:41.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明天要来我家留宿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:43.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:50.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:51.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:55.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥我会在做过夜的准备啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:59.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘好像也有喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.33,0:20:04.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们俩干脆来个通宵girls talk怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:05.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.17,0:20:09.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会在同一张床上睡觉什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.47,0:20:19.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊，结果只是跟小绘关系好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:24.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦 有小绘就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.17,0:20:31.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都是女生 不知道有什么打算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:33.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,女生聚会？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:34.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:39.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:42.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:45.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:51.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为都是女生 才能那么随意的在彼此家中留宿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:55.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能比平时更靠近她一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:57.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不就够幸运的了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:21:00.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 乐观点乐观点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:04.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:08.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是那样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:09.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.09,0:21:10.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:13.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还是做了这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:17.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:19.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆死了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:21.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我这种人
